data.description: Here is a great opportunity to on this three bedroom two bath home in the well-established neighborhood of Ridgeview Acres in Henryville, Indiana. This home features an open concept with a split floor plan and a large eat-in kitchen with lots of cabinetry, counter space, and a kitchen island. Make yourself at home with the large master bedroom and walk-in closet and large owner suite bathroom. Tile flooring and laminate flooring throughout. Fully fenced in backyard with a large deck for entertaining and a shed that stays with the sale. Large two car garage. The price for this house is hard to beat in northern Clark County for $240,000. No money down to those who qualify through the USDA Rural housing loan option. Call today to see this great home!
